> Here are some possible (and trivial) cleanups.
> - use kzalloc() where possible
> - invert allocation failure test like
>   if (object) {
>         /* Rest of function here */
>   }
>   to
> 
>   if (object == NULL)
>         return NULL;
> 
>   /* Rest of function here */
> 
> Signed-off-by: Ingo Oeser <ioe-lkml@rameria.de>
